OVER!"}}},"lobby":{"M":{"game_options_label":{"S":"Game Options"},"how_to_play":{"S":"And now, it’s time for the game show where it’s important to know what things are, it’s TIP OF THE TONGUE!

How to play is very simple. You and your friends will be playing together in this fast-paced game where you try to get as many words right as you can within the time limit.

In the lobby screen you can choose whether to use double rounds which gives each player two chances as the guesser. You can also select how long the rounds are - we recommend longer rounds for your first few games!

On your turn, your friends will shout out clues to the word that they see in the category of your choice and get you to guess it. If you get the word right, then any of your teammates can mark it as scored. If you aren’t getting anywhere with the word, you can choose to skip the word and lose a point.

And if you need added incentive to do your best, the person who gets the most words right is the MVP and gets extra bragging rights!
